com.simbachain.simba

Class CallResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simbachain.simba.CallResponse
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CallReturn

    public class CallResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    The return value of a call to a method using POST. The response contains a unique request identifier. This can either be an ID generated for the request, or a transaction hash associated with the request if the request is creating a transaction.

    Additionally the response may contain a state attribute and an error string.
